== Using Lastfmsubmitd

=== *Configuring Lastfmsubmitd*

Change your LastFM username and password in /etc/lastfmsubmitd.conf
and the MPD server settings in /etc/lastmp.conf before starting the LastFM submit daemon.


=== *Starting the daemon(s)*

After configuring lastfmsubmitd, you should run the following commands
to start the daemons.

-----------------------------
# service lastfmsubmitd start
# service lastmp start
-----------------------------
